24T18:31:07.000Z","msg":"唔食野好耐都唔會死既，<br />\n每星期捉佢出黎飲下水啦"},{"pid":"f15661e6520bb617659a9e31d52b056e21eb4a88","tid":133552,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:31:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我養左兩隻差唔多8-10年<br />\n都無乜見佢地唔食野</blockquote><br />\n我養果兩隻早幾年仲會冬眠時，真係完全唔駛食<br />\n<br />\n近兩年都冇見過佢地冬眠了，愈食愈大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3126c30480de80906642672590f8bc1aeecb16db","tid":133552,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我養左兩隻差唔多8-10年<br />\n都無乜見佢地唔食野</blockquote><br />\n係咪太細粒"},{"pid":"04d39baef595bf621b9a5c9894a8bc179319da5a","tid":133552,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔食野好耐都唔會死既，<br />\n每星期捉佢出黎飲下水啦</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6042e0789d796e6e7b8d30b34a6c31292c9ee263","tid":133552,"uid":87139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我養左兩隻差唔多8-10年<br />\n都無乜見佢地唔食野</blockquote><br />\n我養果兩隻早幾年仲會冬眠時，真係完全唔駛食<br />\n<br />\n近兩年都冇見過佢地冬眠了，愈食愈大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我呢兩隻都係<br />\n以前冬天怕水凍就用唔著既衫冚住佢地<br />\n可以瞓勁耐<br />\n依家就掛住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ea918d7d24a8e4a4b7aca49327d784e8ece9fd","tid":133552,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我養左兩隻差唔多8-10年<br />\n都無乜見佢地唔食野</blockquote><br />\n我養果兩隻早幾年仲會冬眠時，真係完全唔駛食<br />\n<br />\n近兩年都冇見過佢地冬眠了，愈食愈大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我呢兩隻都係<br />\n以前冬天怕水凍就用唔著既衫冚住佢地<br />\n可以瞓勁耐<br />\n依家就掛住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有用手巾蓋"},{"pid":"eb58c38b841fde6a9bd5c932242b474b27cfbc87","tid":133552,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我養左兩隻差唔多8-10年<br />\n都無乜見佢地唔食野</blockquote><br />\n我養果兩隻早幾年仲會冬眠時，真係完全唔駛食<br />\n<br />\n近兩年都冇見過佢地冬眠了，愈食愈大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我呢兩隻都係<br />\n以前冬天怕水凍就用唔著既衫冚住佢地<br />\n可以瞓勁耐<br />\n依家就掛住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毛</span></span>巾蓋</blockquote>"},{"pid":"95d267d873133dee86c94eb852aed060c0e00b27","tid":133552,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:05:18.000Z","msg":"買暖管咪得囉"},{"pid":"f020f5aae8ec969154faa37d9ec72fcee1b72816","tid":133552,"uid":52597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"未夠凍冬眠，又未夠熱活動，咪唔食嘢囉<br />\n<br />\n冬天保温嘅話，日頭用十幾廿蚊嘅菲記射膽加温，夜晚用爬蟲紅膽或者陶瓷膽，再加支暖管喺水度<br />\n<br />\n不過凍天都就快過啦，等多一兩個禮拜就暖返<br />\n<br />\n水龜乾養太耐個殻會變形，仲有龜係冷血動物，冚毛巾係幫唔到佢保暖"}]}